        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Primary Care Enhancement Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill permits a taxpayer with a primary care service arrangement whose fixed periodic fee&nbsp;does not exceed $150 a month to participate in and contribute to a health savings account.</p>]]>
        </text>
